We should be busting the doors down to get into church. Don't be stoic; come out charged.

00:49:13.754 --> 00:50:55.264
We need to create an atmosphere for the Holy Spirit in our houses through worship.

00:50:55.265 --> 00:52:16.272
I'm thankful for being born for such a time as this. You are an inferno, not just a little light.

00:52:16.273 --> 00:52:20.118
You can't be a part-time Christian fighting a full-time devil.

00:52:20.119 --> 00:54:27.623
We're believing for 100,000 people to pray every day. I know people are desperate, but don't give up on yourself.

00:54:27.624 --> 00:55:07.112
Joy comes in the morning. The storm won't last. You're on the one-yard line, fixing to make a touchdown.

00:55:07.113 --> 00:57:08.376
Push harder. Sing 'Because He Lives'to face tomorrow. Life is worth living just because he lives.

00:57:08.377 --> 00:58:11.358
We love you and pray for you. Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:58:11.359 --> 00:58:23.240
God bless you all. We'll be here tomorrow for day 56. Bye-bye.

